subSubSection.paragraph:
Parameres (
Fig. 12–13
) short, barely sinuate along sides, latero-apical spatulae bent ventrally, not or very slightly diverging apically, without latero-proximal denticle, latero-apical angle round. Lamella copulatrix (
Fig. 14
) horseshoe shaped and clearly emarginate at one side, right lobe with a strongly sclerotized plica ventrally bent.
